Hereâ€™s a fully functional calculator app built with **Next.js**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Shadcn**. The app includes a clean and intuitive design, and it adheres to professional coding standards. Since the user did not specify a backend requirement, this implementation focuses solely on the frontend.

---

### **Setup Script**
This script sets up the Next.js app with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Shadcn.

```bash
